Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.56,0:03:36.49,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\an9}捕捉那交錯的視線
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.59,0:03:41.55,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\an8}喜歡我嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.91,0:03:44.93,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\an8}拜託了  Bitter  Tune
