Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,------------SUB-----------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.15,0:00:10.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那個  乃木坂同學很瞭解男性的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.99,0:00:15.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪…哪裡有  一般般而已
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.17,0:00:21.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請不用謙虛  我曾經得到過你的好建議
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.27,0:00:23.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在班裡也大受好評哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.17,0:00:27.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真是無所不知呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.39,0:00:29.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才…才沒有啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.00,0:00:33.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那個  其實我…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.87,0:00:39.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被一位男性邀請去約會了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.24,0:00:40.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約…約會？！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.17,0:00:41.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.71,0:00:46.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然是從很早前就彼此熟識的人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.60,0:00:49.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但卻是第一次邀請我約會
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.58,0:00:51.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.42,0:00:57.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃木坂同學  請問約會時到底要做些什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.60,0:00:58.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.53,0:01:00.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.62,0:01:03.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了今後的打算請你賜教
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.32,0:01:06.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請告訴我吧  乃木坂同學
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.13,0:01:08.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.31,0:01:13.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.20,0:01:17.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天就特別指導你們一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.30,0:01:19.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.36,0:01:20.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.65,0:01:24.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在恬靜的咖啡店中邊品嚐紅茶邊談笑
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.89,0:01:26.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這應該是個不錯的主意
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.56,0:01:30.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面對面坐著  彼此注視的話
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.99,0:01:33.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就連時間的流逝都能忘懷
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.99,0:01:35.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彼  彼此注視…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.05,0:01:37.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太大膽了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.65,0:01:40.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那之後就可以兩人一起去散步
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.90,0:01:45.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然  要溫柔地牽著手
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.30,0:01:46.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牽  牽著手？！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.34,0:01:48.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可以  太不像話了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.42,0:01:52.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不  兩人是戀人的話就無須介意
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.32,0:01:56.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後去電影院之類的也不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.51,0:01:57.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電影院
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.80,0:02:00.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在安靜的地方  兩人互相依偎的話
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.62,0:02:07.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩人的氣氛將會與電影一起達到最高潮
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.28,0:02:10.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且在這種季節裡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.17,0:02:13.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還能在約會的最後兩人去祭典和煙花大會
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.93,0:02:15.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在遊玩了店攤後
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.50,0:02:18.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觀賞在夜空中綻放的美麗煙花
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.05,0:02:23.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩人在此接下第一吻…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.35,0:02:26.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我已經不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.56,0:02:28.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是受益匪淺了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.62,0:02:30.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.43,0:04:07.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然順勢就說了那種話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.24,0:04:10.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我也沒約會過啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.98,0:04:17.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀  因為美夏小姐能看得上眼的男性少得可憐嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.47,0:04:19.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該說根本就沒機會相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.30,0:04:23.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學校又是只有大小姐的女子學校
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.31,0:04:25.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上學放學都是專車接送
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.35,0:04:31.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要說我身邊的男性  也就爸爸和大哥哥了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.15,0:04:36.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是我也像姐姐那樣選普通的學校就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.24,0:04:38.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.87,0:04:41.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香小姐自從夏漫展事件後
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.29,0:04:43.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感情比以前更積極了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.32,0:04:49.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那父母公認的情侶今天也是約會嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.69,0:04:53.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  裕人先生來訪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.54,0:04:56.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在春香小姐的房裡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.51,0:04:58.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是說…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.17,0:05:02.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  現在是單獨相處中
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.93,0:05:05.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎是嗎  是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.94,0:05:07.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.24,0:05:20.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然我還是無法忍受
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.92,0:05:24.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行哦  不是說好了要相信春香
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.60,0:05:27.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不干涉他們的事了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.48,0:05:28.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可  可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.90,0:05:32.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓年輕的男女單獨相處太不純潔了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.33,0:05:36.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你的意思是說我們的女兒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.44,0:05:40.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在做需要瞞著父母的不純潔的事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.50,0:05:43.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…我也不是這種意思
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.26,0:05:47.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我們無關呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.02,0:05:51.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為妹妹擔心姐姐也是理所當然的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.08,0:05:55.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是作為乃木坂家的女僕
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.00,0:05:57.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擔心是理所當然的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.47,0:06:03.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香  可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.59,0:06:07.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但…但是好害羞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.25,0:06:11.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變…變成這樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.57,0:06:13.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再讓我看清楚一點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.51,0:06:16.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不行  那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.13,0:06:18.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的如何
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.26,0:06:23.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常的  大
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.23,0:06:26.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香的也是  這麼熱…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.39,0:06:27.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.98,0:06:29.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.26,0:06:30.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不不不不行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.95,0:06:34.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你們再親熱也還不能做這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.16,0:06:35.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.39,0:06:36.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.50,0:06:38.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美夏？  那波？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.48,0:06:39.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.56,0:06:41.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大哥哥你們才是在幹什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.76,0:06:44.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們只是在做煎餅罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.98,0:06:46.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正馬上就到喝茶的時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.20,0:06:51.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是因為焦了一點  所以有點害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.41,0:06:56.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事啦  我不也做得大過頭了  而且翻面的時候還失敗了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.88,0:06:59.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煎餅…嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.49,0:07:02.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又幹這些讓人誤解的事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.12,0:07:04.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們以為是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.43,0:07:05.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.97,0:07:07.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要深究了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.56,0:07:09.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又做奇怪的猜想了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.22,0:07:13.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經烤好了  要不要一起來吃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.68,0:07:15.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想您肯定會這麼說的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.63,0:07:17.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以準備好了足夠大家的份
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.90,0:07:22.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是葉月  大家一起來吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.97,0:07:31.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸直到昨天為止都還在一個叫五角大樓的地方出差
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.33,0:07:35.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上個月似乎還去了一個叫摩薩德的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.00,0:07:38.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你爸爸是何方神聖啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.83,0:07:43.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後小秋就弄翻了咖喱烏冬面
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.69,0:07:45.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後呢  然後呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.29,0:07:50.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是就在那時大量蔥頭襲來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.36,0:07:53.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才的海藻和麥麩怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.28,0:07:54.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.01,0:07:58.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香  作業完成了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.06,0:08:01.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  差不多了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.67,0:08:02.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.85,0:08:05.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還差很多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.21,0:08:17.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那波  你認為今天姐姐他們如何
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.21,0:08:18.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.26,0:08:22.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我認為非常親密  非常友好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.35,0:08:24.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天真  那波你太天真了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.93,0:08:27.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像將煉乳一口氣喝下一般的天真
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.93,0:08:27.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}註：日語甜和天真發音相同
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.20,0:08:31.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐跨越了特殊愛好的牆壁
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.09,0:08:35.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且不久前還發生了那種事件  也過關了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.13,0:08:37.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是兩人的感情還是沒什麼進展
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.23,0:08:43.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邊吃著煎餅蛋糕邊聊天  氣氛完全起不來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.30,0:08:45.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是非常令人擔憂的狀況
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.23,0:08:51.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐就那個性格  不主動一些也沒什麼可說的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.57,0:08:53.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是問題在於大哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.52,0:08:56.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐那麼可愛  而且條件也都齊全了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.50,0:08:58.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然悠哉地聊天
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.04,0:08:59.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這必須想想辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.52,0:09:00.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.25,0:09:05.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要告訴大哥哥  戀人是怎麼樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.62,0:09:07.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是按計劃行事的話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.24,0:09:08.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩人就會更加親密
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.94,0:09:12.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後將留下甜蜜的夏日回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.15,0:09:15.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美夏小姐太大膽了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.15,0:09:19.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此  馬上展開行動
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.95,0:09:23.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.19,0:09:26.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕人  我是春香
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.78,0:09:27.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是美夏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.29,0:09:31.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你聽出來了啊  不愧是戀人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.63,0:09:33.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.56,0:09:35.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.89,0:09:38.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  有些事想談談
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.99,0:09:40.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這週的星期天有空嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.00,0:09:45.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有空是有空  不過是什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.34,0:09:46.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是非常重要的事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.37,0:09:51.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽到了吧  亂七八糟的很不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.82,0:09:52.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之絕對要來哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.98,0:09:55.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那星期天10點在車站見  就這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.71,0:10:02.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊…剛才那是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.97,0:10:09.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天那個…那到底是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.32,0:10:12.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太慢了  竟然讓女孩子等你  完全不行哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.43,0:10:15.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是姐姐的話該如何是好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.94,0:10:17.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.85,0:10:19.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且你這打扮算什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.91,0:10:21.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全是你平常穿的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.76,0:10:25.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是約會  就應該穿好一點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.84,0:10:27.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼  約會？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.70,0:10:30.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  今天是我和大哥哥的約會
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.98,0:10:35.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對我進行約會的指導？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.78,0:10:38.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  在旁邊看得我著急死了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.00,0:10:41.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐又像那樣非常遲鈍
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.13,0:10:47.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我想只有讓大哥哥積極起來才行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.63,0:10:49.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多管閒事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.84,0:10:51.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這話算什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.64,0:10:55.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難得我為了你們而幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.43,0:10:59.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歸根到底  大哥哥你就滿足現狀了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.06,0:11:02.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難得出來玩一次  卻光是在聊天
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.64,0:11:06.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又形不成好氣氛  一天就結束了說拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.23,0:11:07.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直都是這樣的關係也行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.80,0:11:09.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.29,0:11:11.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是你想等姐姐行動的話就會一直這樣哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.03,0:11:14.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是男人的話該出手時就出手  該幹就幹
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.10,0:11:19.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為此我才來傳授你戀愛的奧義
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.13,0:11:22.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戀愛的奧義啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.00,0:11:26.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如說進了這種氣氛好的咖啡店的話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.24,0:11:28.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就不用聊動畫和作業的事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.79,0:11:30.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是互相注視著
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.32,0:11:34.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.19,0:11:46.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要崩了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.44,0:11:51.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.55,0:11:53.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.78,0:11:58.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像剛才那樣保護好的話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.54,0:12:01.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是遲鈍的姐姐也會心跳不止的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.59,0:12:04.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.03,0:12:11.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行了  不合格
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.97,0:12:13.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.98,0:12:16.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種時候就該牽起手
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.27,0:12:19.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.42,0:12:23.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好  跟姐姐的時候要大哥哥主動去牽哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.17,0:12:25.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危險
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.49,0:12:30.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧  美夏
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.05,0:12:34.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  剛…剛才還挺不錯的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.97,0:12:38.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那快點繼續吧  接下來是看電影哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.52,0:12:41.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大哥哥快點
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.60,0:12:42.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.93,0:12:56.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請放棄您的這份思念吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.27,0:13:00.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  輝夜姬  如果是為了您的話  就算是蓬萊之地…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.76,0:13:02.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在電影院裡該怎麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.65,0:13:05.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩人靠在一起  總之要依偎著
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.04,0:13:08.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是在看電影  也告訴姐姐你的心是向著她的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.50,0:13:10.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊  我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.77,0:13:21.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不好不好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.03,0:13:26.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教人的人怎麼先睡著了  這該如何是好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.32,0:13:29.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊～  不行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.88,0:13:31.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種地方…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.69,0:13:33.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭～大哥哥好色哦～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.98,0:13:35.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什  什  什…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.89,0:13:37.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美夏  好害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.89,0:13:43.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美夏  我說你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.32,0:13:47.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那是為了讓你引以為戒而作的失敗的範例
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.51,0:13:48.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.69,0:13:50.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  接下來我們去哪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.94,0:13:53.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來  我們去參加河邊的煙花大會
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.60,0:13:55.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次我把姐姐也叫上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.98,0:13:56.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.87,0:13:57.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.54,0:13:59.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說是日本舞的練習結束以後  就會過來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.72,0:14:02.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會見機行事  讓你們倆獨處的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.49,0:14:04.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要好好把握機會哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.02,0:14:06.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然你這麼說…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.91,0:14:08.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之  我盡力而為吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.02,0:14:10.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  我們出發吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.15,0:14:12.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.45,0:14:15.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是說要牽著手嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.99,0:14:19.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…對  做得不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.09,0:14:20.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.95,0:14:29.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然週日人很多啊  小心不要走散了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.04,0:14:33.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他這是在擔心我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.44,0:14:36.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  這不是裕人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.85,0:14:38.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好啊  椎菜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.68,0:14:40.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在幹什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.52,0:14:43.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  這不是乃木坂同學的妹妹嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.69,0:14:47.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼  什麼  今天和妹妹兩人約會嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.36,0:14:49.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都有了我你還這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.59,0:14:52.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不要說這種讓人誤會的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.66,0:14:54.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天有點事情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.68,0:14:56.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯～  是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.81,0:14:59.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,椎菜  接下來要去廟會嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.84,0:15:03.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  去看每年一度的河邊煙花大會
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.30,0:15:03.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.35,0:15:05.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這身浴衣  真不錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.86,0:15:06.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧  對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.51,0:15:08.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可是我最中意的一款
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.45,0:15:15.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惜難得穿一回浴衣  但看的人卻全是女生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.37,0:15:16.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二學期開始以後
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.70,0:15:19.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男生們還會記得我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.72,0:15:23.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題的  如果忘記了的話  到時候我會幫你的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.98,0:15:25.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  謝謝你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.49,0:15:28.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  煙花大會  裕人你們也一起來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.84,0:15:29.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實我們…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.84,0:15:30.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.90,0:15:31.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  美夏
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.27,0:15:34.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是怎麼了  真奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.00,0:15:36.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  喂…到底怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.06,0:15:37.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,預定變更
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.01,0:15:38.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.85,0:15:39.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.07,0:15:47.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  明明有我在旁邊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.61,0:15:49.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那兩個人還談的那麼開心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.22,0:15:53.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說  我和他們不同校  也不同年級
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.74,0:15:57.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是今天是我和大哥哥在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.87,0:16:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  但是為什麼我會生氣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.39,0:16:04.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  這身衣服…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.06,0:16:05.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.32,0:16:11.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇～挺合身的  看上去感覺不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.29,0:16:12.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.98,0:16:14.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說  比起這個
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.65,0:16:19.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有什麼感想要發表嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.36,0:16:24.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浴衣很適合你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.06,0:16:25.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.13,0:16:28.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過還要別人提醒  扣分哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.42,0:16:32.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是姐姐的話  記得要立刻誇獎哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.35,0:16:33.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.88,0:16:34.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.32,0:16:37.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去參加煙花大會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.47,0:16:39.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.59,0:17:18.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢噢  真壯觀啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.30,0:17:22.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.01,0:17:23.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.88,0:17:25.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這樣的話  看不見煙花吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.75,0:17:28.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.67,0:17:33.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用客氣  難得的煙花看不見就太可惜了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.71,0:17:35.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.53,0:17:38.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣如何
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.60,0:17:43.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  一清二楚哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.03,0:17:44.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.30,0:17:52.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後這裡很完美哦  這樣的話一定能和姐姐進展順利的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.66,0:17:54.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  抱歉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.10,0:17:56.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼大哥哥要道歉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.73,0:18:01.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然麻煩你教了我很多  我卻不得要領給你添了很多麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.52,0:18:03.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事  沒有這種事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.65,0:18:07.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原本就是我想出來的怪念頭
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.82,0:18:10.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且  我今天也很開心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.20,0:18:11.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美夏
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.51,0:18:14.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是頭一次約會
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.95,0:18:18.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然發生了不少事  但是大哥哥很溫柔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.29,0:18:23.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是  和美夏一起度過的一天很開心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.83,0:18:24.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.81,0:18:26.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.51,0:18:34.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你太溫柔了  被你這樣說的話我…我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.11,0:18:37.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕…裕人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.17,0:18:44.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒  沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.24,0:18:46.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕人～
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.99,0:18:52.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.26,0:18:54.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.25,0:18:58.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煙花大會還沒結束吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.18,0:19:00.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  接下來才是高潮呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.48,0:19:01.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.47,0:19:05.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊  春香這套浴衣很適合你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.91,0:19:08.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.65,0:19:10.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我最中意的一套
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.56,0:19:12.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那差不多該放我下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.91,0:19:13.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.49,0:19:17.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐也過來了  也不能就一直這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.38,0:19:20.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  下來的話就看不見煙花了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.47,0:19:21.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我並不介意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.07,0:19:24.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不是這個問題啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.23,0:19:25.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.61,0:19:32.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  好漂亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.43,0:19:37.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天玩得可真開心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.70,0:19:40.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那波…莫非你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.08,0:19:43.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣開心的美夏小姐  我還是頭一次見到
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.53,0:19:45.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.89,0:19:47.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒…沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.13,0:19:48.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快…快看煙花
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.95,0:19:50.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.97,0:19:51.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.04,0:19:59.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.39,0:20:12.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家 早上好酸乳
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.17,0:20:15.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家暑假過得愉快嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.66,0:20:16.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.85,0:20:18.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.96,0:20:21.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師…老師
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.03,0:20:24.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三天前被甩了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.42,0:20:28.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太過分了  明明是對方邀請的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.09,0:20:32.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正…反正像我這種…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.48,0:20:38.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老…老師  抱怨就到這  差不多該班會了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.39,0:20:43.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是  就算再怎麼消沉也無濟於事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.48,0:20:44.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然分手了  找下一位就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.02,0:20:46.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由香里  我會努力的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.71,0:20:51.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.36,0:20:54.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輪到今年文化祭的時節了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.57,0:21:01.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後呢  各個班級都要選出男女各一名作為文化祭執行委員
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.80,0:21:04.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有誰想當候選人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.22,0:21:13.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是呢  作為班裡的節目負責人和聯絡人很麻煩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.41,0:21:15.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  我要當執行委員
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.14,0:21:22.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要當執行委員
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.40,0:21:25.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛轉學過來  想要快些融入班級裡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.27,0:21:29.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是積極參加這種學校活動比較快
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.18,0:21:32.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真了不起  天宮同學
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.28,0:21:35.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼男生的話  裕君就麻煩你了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.45,0:21:37.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  為什麼要我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.52,0:21:40.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為兩人看上去關係蠻不錯的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.51,0:21:41.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且座位也緊挨著
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.87,0:21:43.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就幫幫天宮同學吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.49,0:21:46.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為報答  老師我給你做舒服的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.99,0:21:47.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.16,0:21:51.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕人  如果是裕人的話
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.82,0:21:53.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也很贊同
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.97,0:22:00.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕人  裕人  裕人  裕人  裕人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.74,0:22:04.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕人  裕人  裕人  裕人  裕人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.47,0:22:06.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了  如果我可以的話
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.51,0:22:08.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎  謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.42,0:22:11.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼就這樣決定了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.01,0:22:15.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼兩位  上台來和大家打招呼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.35,0:22:15.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.54,0:22:23.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次作為文化祭執行委員的  天宮椎菜
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.07,0:22:29.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姓名寫作  天氣的天  宮成縣的宮  椎樹的椎  菜葉的菜
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.76,0:22:33.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,座右銘是  先發制人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.19,0:22:36.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請大家多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.13,0:24:20.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宇宙歷前793年  帝國歷前1103年
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.33,0:24:24.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綾瀨裕人成為了文化祭的執行委員
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.31,0:24:27.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是這只不過是新爭鬥的開幕而已
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.89,0:24:30.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回  乃木坂春香的秘密  第九話
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.97,0:24:32.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很開心哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.35,0:24:34.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,銀河的歷史  又翻開了新的一頁
